[[Tag:3.3]]
= Service Level Support =
* supported AWS services in AWS SDK for Java & Eucalyptus
* S3:  Simple Storage Service
* EC2
* IAM:  Identity and Access Management
* STS:  Simple Token Service

* forthcoming AWS service support in Eucalyptus
* ELB:  Elastic Load Balancing
* CloudWatch
* Autoscaling

* AWS services unsupported in Eucalyptus
* Dynamo
* SimpleDB
* SQS:  Simple Queueing Service
* SNS:  Simple Notification Service
* RDS:  Relational Database Service
* Route 53
* SWS:  Simple Workflow Service
* Elastic MapReduce
* SES:  Simple Email Service
* CloudSearch
* CloudFront
* CloudFormation
* Elastic Beanstalk
* Import/Export
* SGS:  Storage Gateway Service
* ElastiCache
  
= Request Protocols =
* Request Protocols
* Authorization Protocols
